1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,399
Under the combined eruption of the seven Dou Saints,

2
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:09,839
the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame was finally sealed.

3
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:15,239
And with it, the fragile agreement between Xiao Yan and the various factions vanished.

4
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:18,599
The scramble for the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame officially began.

5
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:19,999
In the chaos,

6
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:24,079
Xiao Yan defeated Hun Feng and successfully seized the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame.

7
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,199
But then...

8
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:27,679
the Hall Chief of the Soul Hall, Hun Mie Sheng, suddenly struck.

9
00:00:28,040 --> 00:00:30,959
Yet that was exactly what Xiao Yan had been waiting for.

10
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:33,359
A destructive fire lotus

11
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:35,879
had been ready for a long time.

12
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,280
Xiao Yan!

13
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:45,040
Brother Xiao Yan!

14
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,159
This brat actually wants to take me down with him!

15
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:53,559
he fused Heavenly Flame is indeed powerful.

16
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:56,079
but with Xiao Yan’s own strength...

17
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,279
there’s no way he can kill the Hall Chief.

18
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,079
Brother Xiao Yan!

19
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,280
Are you hurt?

20
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,480
I’m fine.

21
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,720
Sorry for worrying everyone.

22
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,080
Are you trying to get yourself killed?!

23
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,959
If you’d been caught in that blast,

24
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,639
the fire lotus would’ve destroyed you too!

25
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,760
Thank you.

26
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:30,719
Unfortunately...

27
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,479
that still wasn’t enough to finish him.

28
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:43,039
As expected of the one who’s repeatedly foiled my Soul Hall.

29
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,640
You want a fight?

30
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,399
I’ll gladly oblige.

31
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:51,599
You all thought you’d figured out my true strength when we teamed up earlier.

32
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,079
If that were really the case...

33
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,520
then right now,

34
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,759
it’s time to give you all a little surprise.

35
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,720
Five-star Dou Saint...

36
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,559
That old ghost actually tricked us all!

37
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,319
He’s been hiding his real strength this whole time!

38
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,320
Hun Mie Sheng...

39
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,399
You’ve reached five-star Dou Saint and still dare to act?

40
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:38,759
Do you intend to trample the ancient clans’ agreement underfoot?

41
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:42,719
I’ve merely taken half a step into that realm.

42
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,599
It can hardly be considered breaking the agreement.

43
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,319
Hand over the origin of the demonic flame.

44
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:50,440
In your dreams!

45
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,719
The Taixu Ancient Dragon may be powerful,

46
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,239
but challenging this Hall Chief...

47
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,759
is still far too naive.

48
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,199
Sealing the demonic flame consumed too much energy.

49
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,599
Even if we join forces now,

50
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,119
I’m afraid we still can’t deal with him.

51
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,520
Today,

52
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:26,079
this Hall Chief will not let you escape.

53
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,920
Be careful!

54
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,400
Stay out of my way!

55
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,040
Brat...

56
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,120
Prepare to die!

57
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,159
My descendant...

58
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,479
is not someone you can kill on a whim.

59
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,520
Ancestor Xiao Chen!

60
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,799
You’ve broken the fire slave imprint?

61
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,320
While the demonic flame was sealed,

62
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,159
I took the time to erase it.

63
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,600
Ancestor...

64
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,879
You’re from the Xiao Clan?

65
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,040
Soul Clan vermin,

66
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,439
cease your barking.

67
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,480
Mid five-star...

68
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Ancestor... he actually...

69
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,719
Who exactly are you?

70
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,320
If you truly belong to the Xiao Clan,

71
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,479
the Soul Clan should have some information on you.

72
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,119
Enough of your nonsense!

73
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,760
Not good...

74
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,239
Heaven-Splitting Three Axes!

75
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,279
Soul Burial Shield!

76
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:15,919
Ancestor Xiao Chen’s strength is actually this terrifying...

77
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,639
No wonder he could last so long in the illusion realm.

78
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,119
You’re quite tough.

79
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:27,640
Old Demon,

80
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,680
you’ve been watching the show long enough.

81
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:29,999
Time to make your move, no?

82
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,639
And the Soul Clan as well...

83
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,439
Hun Mie Sheng,

84
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:44,879
you’ve truly disappointed this old man.

85
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,479
Soul Demon Elder...

86
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,559
The Soul Clan actually sent you out here.

87
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:01,399
Are you truly intent on tearing all ties with the ancient clans?

88
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,960
Ridiculous.

89
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:08,159
In front of the origin of the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame, what are you all worth?

90
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,160
I knew it.

91
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:32,599
Your Soul Clan would never play by the rules.

92
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,120
This aura...

93
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,760
Ox...

94
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,239
Disciple greets the Old Ancestor.

95
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,199
You’re Little Mo, right?

96
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,400
It’s been many years.

97
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,759
You’ve become a Dou Saint now.

98
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,959
It’s all thanks to the guidance you gave me back then, Old Ancestor.

99
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,639
Only then was I able to break through.

100
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:12,199
Old monster from the Little Pill Tower...

101
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:15,279
You still love putting on this mysterious act.

102
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,879
If the Soul Clan had followed the rules,

103
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,839
I wouldn’t have needed to show myself.

104
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,439
The origin of the demonic flame...

105
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,319
belongs to my Soul Clan now.

106
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,439
You’d best stay out of it.

107
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,679
Otherwise, our Clan Chief

108
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:31,599
won’t mind claiming that peak nine-grade Mystic Pill of yours.

109
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,759
He’s had his eye on me for more than a day or two.

110
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,799
But if I deliver myself to his mouth,

111
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,999
would he even dare to take a bite?

112
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:47,239
The Xiao Clan really is like a centipede—
still wriggling even after it’s dead.

113
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:50,079
Blood Axe Xiao Chen actually managed to survive until now.

114
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,279
That’s quite something to celebrate.

115
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,119
Blood Axe Xiao Chen...

116
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,640
It’s actually him.

117
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,840
Truly...

118
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,160
it’s been a long time.

119
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,359
Alright.

120
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,559
Now is not the time for catching up.

121
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,679
Xiao Yan,

122
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,639
hand over the origin of the demonic flame.

123
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,399
This aura...

124
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:12,839
It’s the senior who saved me from Hun Mie Sheng earlier.

125
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,439
Old Ancestor,

126
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,000
catch!

127
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,639
I’ll hold onto it for you.

128
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,200
Spatial Shift!

129
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,680
Six-star Dou Saint...

130
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,119
The Little Pill Tower actually has a six-star Dou Saint!

131
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,359
No wonder my Soul Hall’s repeated attempts to move against the Pill Tower

132
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,919
were always stopped by the clan.

133
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,759
An expert of this level

134
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,359
is extremely rare even within our own clan.

135
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,159
Pure Lotus Demonic Flame,

136
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,639
you allowed yourself to be sealed on purpose,

137
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,279
just to watch us fight among ourselves

138
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,439
so you could reap the benefits in the end, right?

139
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,439
You hid yourself well,

140
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,720
but you can’t hide from me.

141
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,240
Come out!

142
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,799
If you refuse to show yourself willingly,

143
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,519
then I’ll have to force you out.

144
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,360
Old monster,

145
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,600
you’ve ruined my plans again.

146
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:27,920
Are you looking to die?

147
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,400
This guy...

148
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,919
really did let himself get sealed on purpose.

149
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,159
Pure Lotus Demonic Flame,

150
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,559
your nature is violent and cruel.

151
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:36,679
If we let you enter the Central Plains,

152
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,359
you would bring endless slaughter.

153
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,240
That’s why

154
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:43,479
the Pure Lotus Demonic Saint chose to seal you back then.

155
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:44,759
You

156
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,199
cannot leave this place.

157
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:47,640
Don’t mention that old bastard!

158
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,479
I accompanied him for over a thousand years.

159
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,559
Even if I had no merits, I still suffered hardships.

160
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,559
And yet he still wanted to seal me!

161
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,159
Serves him right that he got devoured in return!

162
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:58,559
As for whether I can leave today...

163
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,959
that’s not for you to decide.

164
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,239
Demonic Flame Divine Statue!

165
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,480
Die!

166
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:25,640
Everyone, be careful!

167
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,920
What’s happening?

168
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,519
All of you, go to hell!

169
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:16,560
Pill Melting Heaven!

170
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:42,079
It can actually melt demonic flame...

171
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,719
Today, anyone who dares to stop me from escaping

172
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,079
will be refined alive by me!

173
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,720
And you—

174
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,959
this old ghost whose true form is a pill...

175
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:58,319
I’d like to see what you turn into after I refine you.

176
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,479
Refining Heaven Ancient Array!

177
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,720
Appear!

178
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:25,839
This grand sealing array personally set up by the Pure Lotus Demonic Saint

179
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:28,479
has ultimately been deciphered by me.

180
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:29,759
Now it serves me.

181
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,159
Inside this demonic flame space,

182
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:34,559
who can possibly stand against me?

183
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,039
Not good...

184
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,479
His aura is surging wildly!

185
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,040
Retreat, quickly!

186
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,479
The passage won’t open!

187
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:57,399
This demonic flame space was created by the Pure Lotus Demonic Saint,
the one said to be closest to Dou Di.

188
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:00,639
A space built by such a supreme expert

189
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:03,559
is not something anyone can open a passage through at will.

190
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:08,719
I will refine every last one of you into my fire slaves!

191
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,360
What do we do?

192
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,519
How about we join forces?

193
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,959
The Heaven-Refining Grand Array is divided into two sides—heaven and earth.

194
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,759
We’ll handle the Heaven Array.

195
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,839
You all take the Earth Array.

196
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,640
Follow me!

197
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,159
Everyone,

198
00:14:33,640 --> 00:14:34,640
attack with me!

199
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:39,880
Let’s go too!

200
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,000
Youngster,

201
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,519
lend me your body for a moment.

202
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:49,359
Otherwise today,

203
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:50,959
none of you will escape death.

204
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,679
How dare an ant try to stop a chariot!

205
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,159
Refining Heaven Ancient Array!

206
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,799
Refine the heavens into slaves!

207
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,640
Attack together!

208
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:39,159
Kid,

209
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:40,759
hand over your body to me now!

210
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,839
Once the Refining Heaven Ancient Array is fully activated,

211
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:44,679
you will have no path to survival.

212
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,959
Even if it’s for the lives of the people beside you,

213
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,639
trust this old man just this once.

214
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:58,079
Struggling in vain.

215
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,319
Although I hate that guy with every fiber of my being,

216
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:05,519
if even the grand array he set up could be casually broken by you third-rate amateurs,

217
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:08,439
would I have been trapped here for thousands of years?

218
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:41,520
A thousand years...

219
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:43,199
It’s finally coming to an end.

220
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,600
Pure Lotus Demonic Saint...

221
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:52,959
Do you really think this can destroy me?

222
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:54,839
I am a divine entity of heaven and earth.

223
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,799
Heaven and earth themselves protect me.

224
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:17,920
He’s still alive?

225
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:19,040
How is that possible?

226
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,000
Xiao Yan!

227
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,880
Brother Xiao Yan!

228
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:45,320
Pure Lotus Demonic Flame...

229
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,640
It’s not the Pure Lotus Demonic Flame.

230
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:51,720
He is...

231
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,200
the Pure Lotus Demonic Saint!

232
00:17:58,960 --> 00:17:59,960
Little demon...

233
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:01,839
Long time no see.

234
00:18:01,863 --> 00:18:03,863

